data.text:
Surname Mian.

Family name Mian. (Mian. ) , around the world, is quite a rare surname. The family name Mian. is characteristic of Southern Asia, particularly Pakistan, where it is quite a rare surname. Very seldom, Mian. is the forename as well as the last name.
